headline: GEHC Q2 Deep Dive: Tariff Headwinds and Innovation Pipeline Shape Outlook
summary: Healthcare technology company GE HealthCare Technologies (NASDAQ:GEHC) reported revenue ahead of Wall Street’s expectations in Q2 CY2025, with sales up 3.5% year on year to $5.01 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.06 per share was 15.5% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
